Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,喲  來得挺早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,依舊是家生意慘淡的店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真囉嗦  夜晚可熱鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,之前那張照片是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,說來話長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道這玩意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,NERvGear後繼機型——AmuSphere用的MMO遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這和SAO一樣是VRMMO遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Alf  heim  Online？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,發音應該是愛爾芙海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(367,335)\fsp4}ALfheim
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是妖精的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精的國度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是款很溫和的遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不  似乎不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,完全技能制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,重視玩家技巧  而且推薦PK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,完全技能制？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是不存在等級的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,各種技能反覆使用後只會有一定提升
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而戰鬥靠的則是玩家的運動能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,難度還真高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就相當於沒有劍技卻有魔法的SAO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,據說這款遊戲現在大受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,原因好像是因為能飛起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,能飛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精自然擁有翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說遊戲搭載了什麼飛行引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,習慣後就能自由飛行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那要怎麼控制呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不過好像相當困難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那當然  畢竟要操控人類本沒有的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道是不是運動背部肌肉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,熱賣的遊戲和亞絲娜究竟有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很像…亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然也是這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,快告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:03:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,照片上的是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是遊戲裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在ALfheim  Online裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡好像叫世界樹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在這棵樹的上方有座傳說中的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,玩家分為九大種族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,為最先抵達城堡而展開競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,飛上去不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說有什麼滯空時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因此不能無限飛行下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,五名玩家按體型大小疊羅漢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,像多級火箭般接力飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,行為很蠢  但想法不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管他們連世界樹最底的樹枝也到不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但卻拍到了好幾張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一張拍到了非常怪異的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,鳥籠？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,將那個鳥籠放大到最大解析度後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就得到這張照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:05:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但亞絲娜為什麼會在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,RCT  progress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,明日奈的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,全靠我才得以維持
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,艾基爾  這個遊戲軟體能給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題  你是要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去親眼確認
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可以復活的遊戲算得了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我得先去買主機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,用NERvGear就可以運行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,AmuSphere不過是NERvGear的安全加強版
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要救出亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我們的戰鬥永遠看不到盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  改天在這裡來一次線下聚會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是個笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,還…還以為會噎死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真是個急性子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,吃東西別那麼急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,小直  關於昨晚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧小直我才能重新振作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會把亞絲娜帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:06:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,加油  我也想見見亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你們一定能成為好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那一會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一週後的1月26日  婚禮將在這間病房裡舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會叫你來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次借我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,開始連接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到ALfheim  Online
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,首先請輸入性別和角色名稱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  你就是那位英雄桐人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(407,335)\fsp0}Kirito
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來請決定種族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,請從九大種族中選擇一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就選它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,確定選擇守衛精靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(347,335)\fsp1}Spriggan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,角色樣貌將隨機生成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是否繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.00,SPEC4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,120)\fs19}守衛精靈{\r}\N \N領地位於愛爾芙海姆東北方，\N以古代遺跡為首都。\N敏捷度高以及擅長幻屬性魔法。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,即將傳送至守衛精靈的出生地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,祝您好運
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:46.77,SPEC,,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(500,0)}愛爾芙海姆·中立地帶·古森林\N2025年1月20日
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,前不久才發生過那種倒楣事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:25.68,SPEC3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}野外地圖上無法即時退出。是否退出？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,角色狀態是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,出BUG了？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,技能
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,單手劍
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,飛劍
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,武器防禦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,戰時回復
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,探敵
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,追蹤
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,隱藏
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,夜視
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,增加重量上限
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,疾走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,和SAO內的數值一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這難道是SAO內部？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託一定要有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是我  結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你還認得我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我們又見面了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去吃東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,奇跡是會發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡其實不是SAO裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡叫ALfheim  Online  是另一個遊戲世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡有可能是「刀劍神域」伺服器的備份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(321,335)\fsp-1}Sword Art Online
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,備份？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,基礎程式群和圖形形式都完全一致
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是Cardinal系統的版本稍微有點舊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,原本運營SAO的ARGUS的處理結果是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,將運營交由RECT承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是RECT吸收了ARGUS的技術資產
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,並進行了挪用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但為什麼會有我的個人資料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看爸爸的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這和爸爸在SAO裡使用的角色資料相一致
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可能因為存檔格式幾乎一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以覆蓋了兩個遊戲共通技能的熟練度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來  雙刀流的確沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,至於道具…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看來已經損壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,最好是在惹來檢錯程式之前刪除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.54,SPEC3.5,,0,0,0,,是否刪除全部道具？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.71,SPEC3.5,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}是否刪除全部道具？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那技能熟練度怎麼辦好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,至於技能的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只要人類的遊戲管理員不直接查看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,應該就不會有問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來  我連封弊者都不算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而變成一個純粹的作弊者了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣你現在又是怎樣一個狀況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,用作輔助玩家的模擬人格程式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,屬於導航精靈一類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是變化成精靈時的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還和以前一樣擁有管理員權限嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不  頂多只能進行查閱以及登錄廣域地圖資料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,其實呢  亞絲娜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽她好像在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎麼一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亞絲娜在攻略SAO之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,依然沒有回歸現實世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽到有情報說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在愛爾芙海姆目擊到像亞絲娜的玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經知道了大概的所在位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是一個叫世界樹的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,應該就是它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽就在那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來  我怎麼會來到這片荒涼的森林呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,按理應該傳送到出生地才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是位置訊息損壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,又或者是信號受到了干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,既然那樣  把我送到世界樹附近不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣才能飛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好像能用輔助搖桿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,舉起左手  做出握拳的手勢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,往跟前拉是上升
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,推下去是下降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而左右則是轉彎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,按住按鈕是加速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而鬆開則是減速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,翅膀發光時可以飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,經過一定時間後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,必須讓翅膀休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊  基本明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼  離這裡最近的城鎮是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,西面有屬於風精靈的城鎮——司伊魯班
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(282,335)\fsp1}Sylph
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡就是最…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有玩家在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,莉…莉法  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,加把勁  雷根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只要成功逃到風精靈的領地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,雷根  迴避！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真是煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,萬不得已  做好戰鬥準備
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,打不贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,西格魯特他們肯定已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我會盡量多吸引一些敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,而你要自己想辦法打倒一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我會盡力的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,偶爾也要讓我看看你英勇的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這下能贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋  別停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,雷根
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不要怨我  我只是執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,放下錢和道具  我就網開一面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你裝什麼紳士啊  影宗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒遇上女人當對手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,乾脆把她殺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我就算死也要再帶一個人上路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,誰不怕死亡懲罰就放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脾氣真硬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那就別怪我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,會飛還要懂著陸才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,三個重戰士欺負一個女孩子  也太難看了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,區區一個菜鳥還夠膽跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我就如你所願  讓你死在這
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以用劍砍他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那當然…沒什麼不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,至少對方是有那樣的敵意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那就失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,下一個是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  被囚的女王
